<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SheetPoint - AI Financial Spreadsheet Builder & Decision Engine</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Spreadsheet that thinks. Turn your ideas into financial models, insights, and decisions instantly.">
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Lucide Icons -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <!-- Inter Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                    colors: {
                        brand: {
                            50: '#f0f9ff',
                            100: '#e0f2fe',
                            200: '#bae6fd',
                            300: '#7dd3fc',
                            400: '#38bdf8',
                            500: '#0ea5e9',
                            600: '#0284c7',
                            700: '#0369a1',
                            800: '#075985',
                            900: '#0c4a6e',
                        },
                        accent: {
                            50: '#f0fdf4',
                            100: '#dcfce7',
                            200: '#bbf7d0',
                            300: '#86efac',
                            400: '#4ade80',
                            500: '#22c55e',
                            600: '#16a34a',
                            700: '#15803d',
                            800: '#166534',
                            900: '#14532d',
                        }
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'float': 'float 6s ease-in-out infinite',
                        'pulse-slow': 'pulse 4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite',
                        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.5s ease-out forwards',
                        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.7s ease-out forwards',
                    },
                    keyframes: {
                        float: {
                            '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0px)' },
                            '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)' },
                        },
                        slideUp: {
                            '0%': { opacity: '0', transform: 'translateY(20px)' },
                            '100%': { opacity: '1', transform: 'translateY(0)' },
                        },
                        fadeIn: {
                            '0%': { opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { opacity: '1' },
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 50%, #f0fdf4 100%);
        }
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }
        .hero-gradient {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15) 0%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1) 50%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #10b981);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -12px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15);
        }
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .grid-pattern {
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 24px 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800 antialiased">

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav id="navbar" class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 transition-all duration-300 border-b border-transparent">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16">
                <!-- Logo -->
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer" onclick="window.scrollTo({top: 0, behavior: 'smooth'})">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                        <i data-lucide="sheet" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tight text-slate-900">SheetPoint</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Desktop Menu -->
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
                    <a href="#features" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Features</a>
                    <a href="#how-it-works" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">How it Works</a>
                    <a href="#web3" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Web3</a>
                    <a href="#pricing" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Pricing</a>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Auth Buttons -->
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <button onclick="openModal('signin')" class="hidden sm:flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">
                        Sign In
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="openModal('signup')" class="flex items-center px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-brand-600 hover:from-brand-600 hover:to-brand-700 rounded-full shadow-md shadow-brand-500/20 transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                        Sign Up Free
                    </button>
                    <!-- Mobile menu button -->
                    <button class="md:hidden p-2 text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">
                        <i data-lucide="menu" class="w-6 h-6" id="menu-icon"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Mobile Menu -->
        <div id="mobile-menu" class="hidden md:hidden border-t border-slate-100 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md absolute w-full">
            <div class="px-4 py-4 space-y-3">
                <a href="#features" class="block px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-50">Features</a>
                <a href="#how-it-works" class="block px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-50">How it Works</a>
                <a href="#web3" class="block px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-50">Web3</a>
                <a href="#pricing" class="block px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-50">Pricing</a>
                <div class="pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <button onclick="openModal('signin')" class="w-full px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 rounded-md">Sign In</button>
                    <button onclick="openModal('signup')" class="w-full px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-accent-500 rounded-md">Sign Up Free</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-gradient pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] rounded-full bg-brand-400/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <!-- Badge -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 mb-8 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-700 bg-brand-50 border border-brand-100 rounded-full animate-fade-in">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                    <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-accent-400 opacity-75"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-accent-500"></span>
                </span>
                AI Financial & Decision Engine
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 text-slate-900 animate-slide-up">
                Spreadsheet that <span class="text-gradient">thinks.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                Turn your ideas into financial models, insights, and decisions — instantly.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-16 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                <button onclick="openModal('signup')" class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-accent-500 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/25 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-500/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                    🚀 Try SheetPoint Free
                </button>
                <button class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="play-circle" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Watch Demo
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Hero Visual: Dashboard Preview -->
            <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 -right-4 -bottom-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-accent-400 rounded-2xl blur-2xl opacity-20"></div>
                <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white">
                    <div class="h-10 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 flex items-center px-4 gap-2">
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4 flex-1 h-6 bg-slate-200/50 rounded-md max-w-md mx-auto"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white">
                        <!-- Left: Spreadsheet Grid -->
                        <div class="md:col-span-8 grid gap-3">
                            <div class="flex gap-3 mb-2">
                                <div class="h-8 bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 rounded px-3 flex items-center text-sm text-brand-700 flex-1 shadow-sm">
                                    <span class="text-slate-400 mr-2">💬</span> "Create a 5-year startup financial projection with 3 scenarios"
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2 text-xs">
                                <div class="h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200"></div>
                                <div class="h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-slate-700">2026</div>
                                <div class="h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-slate-700">2027</div>
                                <div class="h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-slate-700">2028</div>
                                <div class="h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-slate-700">2029</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2">
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center px-2 text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">Revenue</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$1.2M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$2.8M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$5.4M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$9.1M</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2">
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center px-2 text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">Expenses</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$0.8M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$1.5M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$2.9M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-700">$4.8M</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2">
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-accent-50/50 rounded border border-accent-200 flex items-center px-2 text-xs text-accent-700 font-bold">Net Profit</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-accent-50/50 rounded border border-accent-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-accent-700 font-bold">$0.4M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-accent-50/50 rounded border border-accent-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-accent-700 font-bold">$1.3M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-accent-50/50 rounded border border-accent-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-accent-700 font-bold">$2.5M</div>
                                    <div class="h-8 bg-accent-50/50 rounded border border-accent-200 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-accent-700 font-bold">$4.3M</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Chart Area -->
                            <div class="mt-2 h-28 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 flex items-end justify-around px-4 pb-2 pt-4 gap-2">
                                <div class="w-1/5 bg-brand-200 rounded-t h-[30%] relative group"><div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-slate-800 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">Y1</div></div>
                                <div class="w-1/5 bg-brand-300 rounded-t h-[45%] relative group"><div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-slate-800 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">Y2</div></div>
                                <div class="w-1/5 bg-brand-400 rounded-t h-[60%] relative group"><div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-slate-800 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">Y3</div></div>
                                <div class="w-1/5 bg-brand-500 rounded-t h-[80%] relative group"><div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-slate-800 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">Y4</div></div>
                                <div class="w-1/5 bg-accent-400 rounded-t h-[95%] relative group"><div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-slate-800 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">Y5</div></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Right: Insight Panel -->
                        <div class="md:col-span-4 space-y-3">
                            <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="brain-circuit" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-500"></i>
                                    <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wider">Decision Insight</h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <div class="h-1.5 bg-slate-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                                        <div class="h-full w-3/4 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-accent-400 rounded-full"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-500">Growth Score: 84/100</div>
                                    <div class="p-2 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded text-[10px] text-amber-800">
                                        ⚠️ Cash runway drops to 6 months in Y3 under Base Case
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="p-2 bg-accent-50 border border-accent-200 rounded text-[10px] text-accent-800">
                                        💡 Raise prices by 12% → Profit ↑ 18%
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="toggle-right" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                                    <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wider">Scenario</h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex gap-1">
                                    <button class="flex-1 py-1 px-2 text-[10px] font-medium bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 rounded border border-brand-200">Best</button>
                                    <button class="flex-1 py-1 px-2 text-[10px] font-medium bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 rounded border border-slate-200">Base</button>
                                    <button class="flex-1 py-1 px-2 text-[10px] font-medium bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 rounded border border-slate-200">Worst</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Social Proof -->
            <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-6 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">Trusted by forward-thinking founders & financial analysts at</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-12 opacity-60 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-700"><i data-lucide="building-2" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Y Combinator</div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-700"><i data-lucide="hexagon" class="w-5 h-5"></i> TechCrunch</div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-700"><i data-lucide="cpu" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Stripe</div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-700"><i data-lucide="shield" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Notion</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/50 border-y border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 reveal">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why financial modeling is broken</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Traditional spreadsheets demand expertise, consume hours, and hide critical risks in complex formulas.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 reveal">
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-red-500 mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-click" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Too Manual</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Hours spent building rows, linking cells, and formatting instead of analyzing strategy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="file-spreadsheet" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Too Complex</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Advanced financial models require deep Excel expertise, creating a bottleneck for founders.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-500 mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Too Slow</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">By the time your model is finished, the market has shifted and your assumptions are outdated.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-rose-500 mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="bug" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Too Many Errors</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">A single broken formula can cascade into millions of dollars in miscalculated runway.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-3xl h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand-200 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center reveal">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Meet your AI Financial Brain</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">SheetPoint transforms raw prompts into structured financial models, extracting actionable insights and clear decisions automatically.</p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-lg font-bold">1</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800">Prompt → Spreadsheet</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1">Describe your business model in natural language. AI structures it into rows, columns, and formulas instantly.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-600 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-lg font-bold">2</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800">Spreadsheet → Insight</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1">The engine scans your data for cash flow traps, growth bottlenecks, and optimization opportunities.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-lg font-bold">3</span>
                            </div>
